   <text>
      <body>
        <div>
            <pb facs="#TL-0558.jpg" n="part4_p084.jpg" xml:id="img_0084" corresp="https://id.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/tillich-lectures/part4_p084.jpg"/>
            
            <p facs="#facs_84_tr_3">
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_3_tl_1" n="N001"/>Monsieur M r de
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_3_tl_2" n="N002"/>-us¬
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_3_tl_3" n="N003"/>Let's go into some of these example. Not many of you are able even to understand why
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_3_tl_4" n="N004"/>a roan like Hitler could become ultimate authority for a whole nation of kompar lively (ducated people)
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_3_tl_5" n="N005"/>He COU Ma because of an Kdeology in which the Grarticipation in this nation was a participation in a
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_3_tl_6" n="N006"/>sacramental unity. I come back to these points later when we speak about conformism, and also
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_84_tr_2">
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_1" n="N001"/>politics. I had a friend, perhaps the most intelligent professor of theology—we studied together¬
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_2" n="N002"/>and when the Nazis came I turned against them and he turned for them. This was an act which
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_3" n="N003"/>for me was hard to understand, but in his very first book, which appeared already in the year 1933,
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_4" n="N004"/>when Hitler came to power, he explained it, and his explanation was of real theological weight
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_5" n="N005"/>and made him the Nazi theologian for the whole period, namely he identified the national community
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_6" n="N006"/>with a Sacramental community. For him, the blood community of the nation had sacramental
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_7" n="N007"/>character. And now he constured Hitler as the voice of God which has the same ultimate authority
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_8" n="N008"/>as the Bible foritzodox Protestants, and the Cope has for orthodox Catholics. The basis was a
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_9" n="N009"/> religious one. And in the moment in which you accept the identity of nation (from the point of
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_2_tl_10" n="N010"/>view of blood, especially, as he did) and sacramental community, then it is quite possible to establish
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_84_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>an authority in principle, namely he through whom the unconscious meaning of this nation speaks,
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>and voice-of-God then means that this unconscious meaning has an ultimate dimension. So we
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>have here an authority which cannot be kriticized any more because it has sacramental conservation.
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>Now let’s take the Protestants. Of course this ultimate authority broke down when it
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_5" n="N005"/>was clear that it was a demonic seduction of the German people into a self-distruction self-elevation
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_6" n="N006"/>*Emanuel Hirsch —Ed.
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_7" n="N007"/>le sujet de cette
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>de votre beau et très obéissant avec
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>lʼhonneur de lʼautreur sérieuse.
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_10" n="N010"/>Gouvernement
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_11" n="N011"/>de mon ami
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_12" n="N012"/>de Votre
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_13" n="N013"/>Monsieur M.
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_14" n="N014"/>Cela nʼentraîne de lʼauteur
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_15" n="N015"/>Votre
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_16" n="N016"/>dʼune manière
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_17" n="N017"/>dʼune manière beaucoup
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_18" n="N018"/>cʼest avec
               <lb facs="#facs_84_tr_1_tl_19" n="N019"/>Monsieur le Comte de lʼéviter
            </p>
            
